texts.text: >A few years earlier. On a sacred mountain somewhere in Tokyo...
*Pant*
I heard that the demons here are strong and came but...
I didn't think they would be this strong.
No, I'm the one who isn't strong enough.
In order to be a fully-fledged member of the Liberators,
and for the sake of my own training, I came here but...
Maybe I was too hasty in starting this "Musha Training"...
*Wince*
>Jeng Yun falls to the ground with a pained expression...
(Everything is going... Dark... This... This is bad...)
Ah, you're awake.
Where am I...? I was on that mountain, lost consciousness and...
This place is the home of the Yamamoto blacksmithing clan.
I found you collapsed out there while wandering around.
So I carried you back here.
It was hardly an easy task. You're very heavy, you know...
Yes, I've been training and gaining quite a bit of muscle.
Allow me to take this off and show you!
As you can see, I've been training very hard!
Hah, so you have!
I came here to train but...
I would've become demon food if no one found me.
I owe you a great debt, so please at least tell me your name.
I am Jogan Yamamoto. I craft enchanted swords based on my ancestors' methods.
>Two women working for the same company are chatting as they walk.
I'm beat. There's so much work to do. What do you feel like for lunch?
I can't spend too much since payday isn't until tomorrow.
Our company's so cheap. We don't get bonuses either, so what the hell...!
>For several weeks now, a dark cloud has hung over Tokyo...
>Its citizens have all become more irritable than usual...
And they treat us like slaves. I mean, listen...
Yesterday, my boss dumped a bunch of work on me and made me stay super late.
And you'd expect a "thank you" or something but...
He just went home without saying a word.
I mean, how screwed up is that? It's just so stressful...
>An advertisement by a Megatuber is being shown on a video wall...
And here we have that new protein! How does it work...?
Man, Megatubers are so lucky. They just talk and roll in the dough.
It's so unfair... While we work our asses of every single day.
>She bumps into a man's shoulder as she walks by...
Hey, what the...?! Watch where you're goin'!
Wait, what?!
What do you mean "what"? Actin' like you own the place.
You're probably just some grunt that has to do what she says, right?

*Laugh*
Enjoy your shitty life, bitch.
What?! Who the hell was that asshole?! He knows nothing about us...
I feel even more tired now... Let's get some food already...
Ugh! I need to write my new story!
But I can't think of anything good! My head's a total mess...!
Ririn, will you please keep it down?
Keep it down? You're the one that doesn't want to help me...
That hardly gives you license to make a big fuss over it.
Everyone's being so prickly, it's making my head hurt...
Hey, will you guys think about how Honey feels too?
Everyone, please calm down. It's not good to fight like this.
Y-You're right... I apologize. I don't know what came over me.
No, I should be apologizing. I'm sorry for all that just now.

*Sigh*
Maybe I'm coming down with something.

*Sigh*
I feel the same. Could it be a cold?
Are you okay?
You should rest.
No, I'm not okay. This isn't just some cold or anything.
Rest? It'll only get worse by doing that too.

*Sigh*
You just don't get it, do you?
It's bad energy. You know, like evil spirits or something?
I can't sense anything like that but...
I experienced something like this in the past.
It feels exactly the same as then.
Yes, I've been more irritable than usual too it seems.
Same. It's like my voice of reason is being suppressed.
An unreasonable Shionyan, who's also having mood swings...!
One more word and I'll...
I'M SORRY!
But you don't seem all that different from usual, Shiori...
I too feel just fine! I've been training after all...
But I've been feeling this change happening too.
It's similar to... High-altitude training...
As in when you train while on top of a mountain or something?
It isn't exactly the same but...
Every action has been taking a greater toll than usual.
And training has given me better muscle definition, so let me show you...!
T-This was his actual goal...!
But yo, some folks have been sayin' that
they're seein' a lot more trolls online too.
Which might mean "she" is gonna make her entrance soon...
Hello, everyone! How are you? I'm doing absolutely awful!
Yo, right on time...
At least it saved us the trouble of calling you.
Oh, so your yearning for me has finally reached the surface?
Not in a million years.
Aww, don't be like that. Anyways...
Does that mean you've all been feeling it too?
Yo, here and there. But that's why we want to talk to you.
Then let's get right to it.
From what I've learned, negative energy began spreading through Tokyo a few days ago.
So far, it's been amplifying everyone's jealousy and doubts,
but if this continues, the whole city will be consumed by these awful feelings.
Consumed? What happens then?
Simply put, Tokyo will be destroyed.
Squabbles will turn into fights, fights into skirmishes, and ultimately...
We'll end up paving our own path to destruction.
With that much negative energy, demons won't sit idly by...
They may even plot to invade and take over the entire city.
Shit. This is worse than I thought...
How we've been feeling has all been because of this energy...?
Yo, it hits folks differently too from what I've seen...
Like altitude sickness, it affects everyone differently...
>There, a man you've never seen before steps through the doorway.
Is this where I can find Jeng Yun?
Yes. I am Jeng Yun. How do you know my name...?
I am here on behalf of Jogan Yamamoto.
